"Now you should already see your reviews. If not, click the 'Pull reviews' "
"button again"
msgstr ""
"Ahora ya deberías ver tus valoraciones. Si no es así, haz clic de nuevo en "
"el botón \"Extraer opiniones\""

#: admin/includes/how-to.php:19
msgid "Hit 'save'"
msgstr "Pulsa \"Guardar\""

#: admin/includes/how-to.php:20
msgid ""
"Use one of the shortcodes in order to display your reviews on pages, posts, "
"Elementor, Beaver Builder, Bakery Builder etc."
